---
description: Krishna Story Factory project rules
alwaysApply: true
---

- Keep this project lightweight and Python-first.
- Do not add Notion, React, FastAPI, PostgreSQL, Docker, Celery, or Redis unless explicitly requested.
- CSV files in `input/` and `tracking/` are the source of truth.
- CLI is the source of truth; Streamlit dashboard is optional UI only.
- Never commit `.env`, API keys, generated outputs, logs, or local outboxes.
- Test mode must not call paid APIs.
- Every generated package must include all nine required outputs.
- Use WhatsApp Business Cloud API for real WhatsApp delivery; do not implement unsafe personal WhatsApp group scraping.
